@@gStorage Annex@@N~
A narrow back room off the main shop corridor, used for overflow stock and supplier correspondence. Crates are stacked against one wall and a writing desk occupies the opposite corner, covered in invoices and packing manifests. The single door to the north is kept locked outside business hours.
